CustomField.description: Select the target object (e.g., Opportunity or CustomChild__c) whose records will be summarized and rolled up to the master object in this job.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enter the API name of the target object (e.g., Opportunity or CustomChild__c) whose records will be summarized and rolled up to the master object in this job. An incorrect or missing API name will prevent the job from executing.
